queries.question: List all films in the 'Action' category
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Action' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List all customers living in 'London'
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name FROM customer c JOIN address a ON c.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE ci.city = 'London';

queries.question: Show full address for each staff member
queries.query: SELECT s.first_name, s.last_name, a.address, ci.city FROM staff s JOIN address a ON s.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id;

queries.question: List all films featuring actor 'PENELOPE GUINESS'
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN film_actor fa ON f.film_id = fa.film_id JOIN actor a ON fa.actor_id = a.actor_id WHERE a.first_name = 'PENELOPE' AND a.last_name = 'GUINESS';

queries.question: List customers who have rented 'ACADEMY DINOSAUR'
queries.query: SELECT DISTINCT c.first_name, c.last_name FROM customer c JOIN rental r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id JOIN inventory i ON r.inventory_id = i.inventory_id JOIN film f ON i.film_id = f.film_id WHERE f.title = 'ACADEMY DINOSAUR';

queries.question: Count number of rentals per customer
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, COUNT(r.rental_id) as rental_count FROM customer c JOIN rental r ON c.customer_id = r.customer_id GROUP BY c.customer_id ORDER BY rental_count DESC LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Count inventory items per film title
queries.query: SELECT f.title, COUNT(i.inventory_id) as stock_count FROM film f JOIN inventory i ON f.film_id = i.film_id GROUP BY f.title ORDER BY stock_count DESC LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List all cities in 'France'
queries.query: SELECT ci.city FROM city ci JOIN country co ON ci.country_id = co.country_id WHERE co.country = 'France';

queries.question: List all store locations (City and Country)
queries.query: SELECT s.store_id, ci.city, co.country FROM store s JOIN address a ON s.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id JOIN country co ON ci.country_id = co.country_id;

queries.question: List actors in the film 'ANGELS LIFE'
queries.query: SELECT a.first_name, a.last_name FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id JOIN film f ON fa.film_id = f.film_id WHERE f.title = 'ANGELS LIFE';

queries.question: List English language films
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN language l ON f.language_id = l.language_id WHERE l.name = 'English' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List films rented by customer with ID 1
queries.query: SELECT f.title, r.rental_date FROM rental r JOIN inventory i ON r.inventory_id = i.inventory_id JOIN film f ON i.film_id = f.film_id WHERE r.customer_id = 1 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List customers associated with Store 1
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name FROM customer c JOIN store s ON c.store_id = s.store_id WHERE s.store_id = 1 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: Find actors with the last name 'DEGENERES' and their films
queries.query: SELECT a.first_name, f.title FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id JOIN film f ON fa.film_id = f.film_id WHERE a.last_name = 'DEGENERES';

queries.question: List films with a replacement cost greater than 20 and their language
queries.query: SELECT f.title, f.replacement_cost, l.name as language FROM film f JOIN language l ON f.language_id = l.language_id WHERE f.replacement_cost > 20 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List active staff members and their store city
queries.query: SELECT s.first_name, s.last_name, ci.city FROM staff s JOIN address a ON s.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE s.active = true;

queries.question: Find films with 'Trailers' as a special feature in 'Action' category
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Action' AND f.special_features::text LIKE '%Trailers%' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List customers in 'London' city
queries.query: SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name FROM customer c JOIN address a ON c.address_id = a.address_id JOIN city ci ON a.city_id = ci.city_id WHERE ci.city = 'London';

queries.question: List films rated 'PG' in 'French' language
queries.query: SELECT f.title FROM film f JOIN language l ON f.language_id = l.language_id WHERE f.rating = 'PG' AND l.name = 'French' LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List rentals processed by Staff ID 1
queries.query: SELECT r.rental_id, r.rental_date FROM rental r WHERE r.staff_id = 1 LIMIT 10;

queries.question: List actors in film 'ZOOLANDER FICTION'
queries.query: SELECT a.first_name, a.last_name FROM actor a JOIN film_actor fa ON a.actor_id = fa.actor_id JOIN film f ON fa.film_id = f.film_id WHERE f.title = 'ZOOLANDER FICTION';

queries.question: List store addresses with postal codes
queries.query: SELECT s.store_id, a.address, a.postal_code FROM store s JOIN address a ON s.address_id = a.address_id;

queries.question: List films with replacement cost under 15 in 'Comedy' category
queries.query: SELECT f.title, f.replacement_cost FROM film f JOIN film_category fc ON f.film_id = fc.film_id JOIN category c ON fc.category_id = c.category_id WHERE c.name = 'Comedy' AND f.replacement_cost < 15 LIMIT 10;
